description.narrative: This activity (Humanitarian Surge Support) is a component of Ethiopia Drought Response Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £838,516. This component benefits Ethiopia, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: CANADEM, Crown Agents Limited, Danish Refugee Council. The start date is 01-04-2016 and the end date is 31-03-2017.
